strings: <voice_0x0100121D><se_high>Jessica: I see you've ignored my advice to prepare a stronger defence!
<voice_0x0100121E><se_def>David: Sh-Shut up! You won't get past me! I won't let you lay a finger on Master Dominico!
<voice_0x01001221><se_high>Jessica: Such a pity...that you should die never knowing about your noble origins...
<voice_0x01001222><se_high>Jessica: I could tell from the start that absurd show-off was not the one! The sceptre is all-knowing!
<voice_0x01001223><se_high>Jessica: No. I seek the chosen heir of the great sage Kupas, one of the seven who sealed away the Lord of Darkness, Rhapthorne...
<voice_0x01001225><se_high>Jessica: What a pity that the one who should be protecting you is unaware of his responsibility!
<voice_0x01001226><se_high>Jessica: Ha ha hah! I wondered when you'd turn up.
<voice_0x01001227><se_high>Jessica: Fine! I knew I'd have to fight you somewhere along the way.
<voice_0x01001228><se_high>Jessica: Still, I have to admit I'll be a little sad to watch you die!
